text: Eadward cyng gret æigelmer biscop & Georð eorl & ealle mine þegenas on æstengle freondlice.

& ic cyðe eou þæt ic habbe geunnen Baldwine abbote onne menetere wið inne Seint Eadmundes byrig al swa freolice on ealle þing to habben al swa me mine on hande stonden ower on enig minre burge alre freolukeost.
